* checkApacheKiller.pl

	Simple Apache Killer checker.

* usage

	perl checkApacheKiller.pl http://example.com/images/sample.jpg

	for virtual host internal

	perl checkApacheKiller.pl http://example.com/images/sample.jpg 127.0.0.1

* EXAMPLE

	$ perl checkApacheKiller.pl http://localhost/images/sample.jpg
	Connect localhost:80
	OK:The host is vulnerable to apache killer

	for japanese
	$ env LANG=ja_JP.UTF=8 checkApacheKiller.pl http://localhost/images/sample.jpg
	Connect localhost:80
	OK:このホストは Apache Killer 対策済みです


